('chk-ml-readiness', 'ph-ml-foundations', 99, 'checkpoint', 'assessment', NULL, NULL, 'ML Baseline Review', 'Review checkpoint for Machine Learning Foundations. The learner consolidates evidence from Supervised vs Unsupervised Learning, Train Validation Test Splits, Bias Variance and Overfitting, Feature Engineering, identifies unresolved prerequisite gaps, and decides whether to continue, review selected topics, or complete extra practice before the next roadmap segment.', 'checkpoint', 2, 'intermediate', '{"reviewFocus":"Review checkpoint for Machine Learning Foundations. The learner consolidates evidence from Supervised vs Unsupervised Learning, Train Validation Test Splits, Bias Variance and Overfitting, Feature Engineering, identifies unresolved prerequisite gaps, and decides whether to continue, review selected topics, or complete extra practice before the next roadmap segment.","reviewCriteria":["List the roadmap items reviewed for this checkpoint.","Provide one evidence artifact such as notes, a diagram, a lab result, code, queries, screenshots, or a project review.","Record at least two gaps, risks, or follow-up actions, or explicitly state that no critical gaps were found.","Use the result to choose one next step: continue, review selected topics, or complete extra practice."],"source":"roadmap.sh/ai-engineer","nodeKey":"chk-ml-readiness"}'::jsonb, true, true, '["Summarize the main concepts and decisions from Machine Learning Foundations in practical AI engineering terms.", "Identify prerequisite gaps, unclear topics, or risks that should be reviewed before moving forward.", "Create a short evidence artifact that links completed roadmap items to what was learned."]'::jsonb, '["List the roadmap items reviewed for this checkpoint.", "Provide one evidence artifact such as notes, a diagram, a lab result, code, queries, screenshots, or a project review.", "Record at least two gaps, risks, or follow-up actions, or explicitly state that no critical gaps were found.", "Use the result to choose one next step: continue, review selected topics, or complete extra practice."]'::jsonb),
